examples.en: She spoke so convincingly that I believed her.
There is no convincing evidence to support his theory.
They make a convincing case for reform.
The results demonstrate convincingly that this method is safe and reliable.
Despite his superstar status, in his movies the actor is able to play the role of an everyman quite convincingly.
He won the election so convincingly that he believed the people had mandated him to carry out his policies.
